                    Studios, or any of their affiliates or subsidiaries.
                    <em>Minecraft Earth™</em> is a trademark of Microsoft Corporation.
                    <br />
                    All trademarks and registered trademarks are the property of their respective owners.
                    <br />
                    This software is provided solely for educational, research, and archival purposes to restore
                    functionality to a discontinued service.
                    <br />
                    This project is provided "as-is" without any warranty of any kind, express or implied. In no event
                    shall the authors be held liable for any claim, damages, or other liability.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>